sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway /<br/>OpenShift Route
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as Drogon HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/2
    participant Handler as API Handler<br/>(TFS/KFS/V3)
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Executor
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime /<br/>GenAI Pipeline
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 / Azure / GCS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local / PVC<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (KServe v2)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>mTLS / Service Identity
    KRBP->>REST: Proxy (authenticated)<br/>HTTP/8080
    REST->>Handler: Route to KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    Handler->>OV: Execute inference<br/>C++ API / protobuf
    OV-->>Handler: Inference result
    Handler-->>REST: protobuf → JSON response
    REST-->>KRBP: HTTP 200 JSON
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completions (OpenAI-compatible, SSE streaming)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v3/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, stream: true
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request
    KRBP->>REST: Proxy to Drogon<br/>HTTP/8080
    REST->>Handler: Route to V3 handler (processV3)
    Handler->>MP: Execute MediaPipe graph
    MP->>OV: OpenVINO GenAI LLM Pipeline<br/>continuous batching
    loop Token Generation (SSE)
        OV-->>MP: Generated token
        MP-->>Handler: Token chunk
        Handler-->>REST: SSE data chunk
        REST-->>KRBP: HTTP chunked
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Stream chunk
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE: data: {...}
    end
    Handler-->>REST: SSE: [DONE]
    REST-->>Client: Stream complete

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 3: gRPC Streaming Inference
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelStreamInfer<br/>HTTP/2, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward gRPC stream
    KRBP->>gRPC: Proxy to gRPC server<br/>8085/TCP
    gRPC->>Handler: KFSInferenceServiceImpl::ModelStreamInfer
    Handler->>MP: Execute streaming MediaPipe graph
    MP->>OV: OpenVINO GenAI pipeline
    loop Streaming Response
        OV-->>MP: Result chunk
        MP-->>Handler: protobuf stream message
        Handler-->>gRPC: gRPC stream response
        gRPC-->>Client: gRPC stream frame
    end

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 4: Model Loading from HuggingFace
    Note right of REST: Triggered by --pull CLI flag at startup
    REST->>Handler: HfPullModelModule start
    Handler->>HF: HTTPS GET model files<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, HF Token
    HF-->>Handler: Model artifacts (weights, config)
    Handler->>FS: Write to local filesystem
    FS-->>Handler: Files written
    Handler->>OV: ServableManager loads model
    OV-->>Handler: Model ready for inference

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 5: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    REST->>Handler: ServableManager model load
    Handler->>S3: HTTPS GET model artifacts<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, IAM credentials
    S3-->>Handler: Model files
    Handler->>OV: Load into OpenVINO Runtime
    OV-->>Handler: Model loaded
